Invocation Name: positive thoughts
des:
Positive thought is a compilation of thoughts that could make your day more positive. If you are feeling sad in your life then after listening these thoughts would make your day. 
This skill motivates you and changes the way you feel about yourself. ... Just as positive words can make someone smile or a well-timed humorous quote can make someone laugh, our thoughts react to the world in real-time.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
